column1: #This table shows promoter locations and annotation information for each promoter. The Tex and Cov (coverage) values for each condition are the average log2 base counts for first 10 transcribed bases at each TSS. The ENR Ratio is the ratio of Tex to coverage base counts indicating Tex enrichment.

column27: fraction of 14 replicates with identical 5' end locations
column28: Criteria scored for promoter confidence score calculation
